{"tid":1662902,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"藍絲都話杯葛有用呀, 你唔係唔跟呀?","createTime":"2019-10-19T05:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T10:21:01.000Z","uid":289751,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"cd7297327c8eb39657907cea5f5f34f0304f2f1e","tid":1662902,"uid":289751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T05:21:45.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】「黃絲」餐廳、「藍絲」集團，最近上街吃飯前，你又會不會先查一查商號的政治立場？被「罷食」的小店，如何應對？<br />\n<br />\n當白領的Charlotte幾個月以來都投入反修例運動，除了上街遊行，她還將抗爭融入生活，現在出外吃飯都要先看看餐廳的政治取向。她認為要找與自己理念相近的餐廳吃飯，雖然要花多點時間，但就會吃得心安理得。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">王莉莉是大埔這間小食店老闆，開業兩年，是被反修例市民杯葛的其中一間店舖。她說被網民號召杯葛之後少了年輕人光顧，收入大減，為了彌補損失，店舖本來星期日休息現在都要營業，而且還要減價，希望薄利多銷。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n公共政策學者葉健民認為，今次反修例運動每個抗爭者都用自己的方法去表達訴求，罷買、杯葛是成本較低的一種。<br />\n<br />\n星期日晚播出的《經緯線》還會看看經過連月示威香港經濟受到怎樣的影響，示威者又係咪「攬炒」成功？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=366767&amp;fbclid=IwAR1zmlNfkKmyCQWlvKzNwmBxb5pfES4AjKzVwzoscYg4JitINkDhw-iZ-Y8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D366767%26fbclid%3DIwAR1zmlNfkKmyCQWlvKzNwmBxb5pfES4AjKzVwzoscYg4JitINkDhw-iZ-Y8&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9h3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=464cbed2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D366767%26fbclid%3DIwAR1zmlNfkKmyCQWlvKzNwmBxb5pfES4AjKzVwzoscYg4JitINkDhw-iZ-Y8&h=08ea05a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=366767&amp;fbclid=IwAR1zmlNfkKmyCQWlvKzNwmBxb5pfES4AjKzVwzoscYg4JitINkDhw-iZ-Y8</a>"},{"pid":"60169c52c012f0e46e08604b72d1144109d3cace","tid":1662902,"uid":108133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T05:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c7e7f68c92c06f3fede607a59f3adf2404424c","tid":1662902,"uid":305349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T05:28:43.000Z","msg":